description:
Massive block of land with lots of potential Look no further if you are looking the best site to do any kind of development. Massive land with total size of 31.32 ha

Located in the main road to Beachmere and in close proximity to a local school, a childcare centre, the beach and a shopping centre which includes an IGA supermarket, medical services, and cafes.

This property also offers a large 3 bedroom house on the ground floor and another upstairs. Both feature spacious living areas with open fireplaces and most rooms opening onto spacious verandas.

Features;

- Currently in the process of obtaining approval to build a brand new 5 bedroom home

- Modern Queenslander design with separate entries for each level
Upstairs comprises spacious living with polished timber floors

- 3 bedrooms, master ensuite plus main bathroom, ceiling fans, air conditioning

- Ground level tiled incl. designer kitchen with gas & electric cooking
3 large bedrooms downstairs, huge bathroom with clawfoot bath & sauna

- 800m to Supermarket, 38 km to Brisbane, 11 km to Caboolture, approx. 30 minutes to Sunshine Coast

For More Information, Please Contact Jun Yang - 0423 275 701
